## Import

An autobackup can be imported using the `project_id` and `id` attributes. Using the following configuration:

{{tffile "examples/resources/cloud_instance_autobackup/example_3.tf"}}

You can then run:

```bash
$ terraform plan -generate-config-out=autobackup.tf
$ terraform apply
```

The file `autobackup.tf` will then contain the imported resource's configuration, that can be copied next to the `import` block above. See https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import/generating-configuration for more details.
